<H4>   Meets Prime Minister Chuan </H4>
<F P=102> BK2803143494 Bangkok Thai Color Television Channel 9 in Thai 
1200 GMT 28 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2803143494 </F>
<F P=104>  Bangkok Thai Color Television Channel 9 </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Thai </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Prince Kromkhun Norodom Sirivut, Cambodian deputy 
prime minister and foreign minister, was accompanied by Foreign 
Minister Squadron Leader Prasong Sunsiri and paid a courtesy 
call on Prime Minister Chuan Likphai at Government House. 
During the meeting, the Cambodian foreign minister thanked 
