relations to the brink of war on the order of the U.S. masters. 
  The South Korean puppet clique are trying to ignite a war 
against the DPRK, following the adventurous war moves of the 
U.S. imperialists. But they would be well advised to mind that 
they would eventfully die a miserable death in the flame they 
kindled. 

