Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vientiane, March 29 (KPL) -- The delegations of the 
Lao Information and Culture Ministry and of the National 
Information Committee of the Democratic People's Republic of 
Korea held talks here yesterday to discuss the mass media role 
in information. 
  Deputy Information and Culture Minister Bouasi Chaleunsouk, 
the head of the Lao side at the talks, told the Korean side 
about the role of the Lao mass media in the task of further 
building and developing the people's democratic regime as well 
