  [Text] Pyongyang, March 30 (KCNA) -- Political party 
leaders of Nepal and Peru fully supported the just cause of the 
Korean people when they met the DPRK ambassadors to their 
countries recently. 
  Man Mohan Adhikari, president of the Central Committee of 
the 
