the Korean people as in the past and fully support the 
self-defensive measures of Korea. 
  Javier Diez Cansenco, general secretary of the Mariateguista 
United Party of Peru, stated that his party will make all 
efforts in support of the Workers' Party, the government and the 
people of Korea in their just struggle against the moves of the 
U.S. imperialists and the International Atomic Energy Agency 
leading the situation on the Korean peninsula to the brink of 
war. 
  Alberto Moreno, general secretary of the Central Committee 
of 
the Communist Party of Peru (Red Motherland), stressed that his 
party will always stand firmly on the side of the Korean people. 

